OL,3,C'Unique' AI-powered headset that can
OL,4,Cpredict epilepsy seizures developed
OL,6,FA "unique" AI-powered headset that can
OL,7,Fpredict epileptic seizures minutes
OL,8,Fbefore they occur has been developed
OL,9,Fby scientists in Scotland.
OL,11,FThe Glasgow Caledonian University team
OL,12,Fbehind the research say the wearable
OL,13,Fdevice could dramatically transform
OL,14,Fthe way the condition is managed.
OL,16,FCurrently, there is no readily
OL,17,Favailable device that can give people
OL,18,Fwith epilepsy advanced warnings of
OL,19,Fseizures.
