OL,3,C'Unique' AI-powered headset that can
OL,4,Cpredict epilepsy seizures developed
OL,6,FThe headset analyses brainwaves and
OL,7,Fheart functions to detect an impending
OL,8,Fseizure, allowing the wearer to take
OL,9,Fprecautions or warn those around them.
OL,11,FThe scientist behind the project says
OL,12,Fits greatest benefit could be giving
OL,13,Fpeople with epilepsy more confidence
OL,14,Fabout the condition, helping them to
OL,15,Favoid any secondary injuries caused by
OL,16,Fa seizure.
OL,18,FHundreds of thousands of people in the
OL,19,FUK live with epilepsy, as well as
OL,20,Fmillions around the world.
