OL,3,C'Unique' AI-powered headset that can
OL,4,Cpredict epilepsy seizures developed
OL,6,FProfessor Hadi Larijani, who leads the
OL,7,Fresearch team at Glasgow Caledonian
OL,8,FUniversity, said: "Providing even a
OL,9,Ffew minutes' warning could be life-
OL,10,Fchanging.
OL,12,F"Our goal is to empower patients and
OL,13,Ffamilies with time to act to stay safe
OL,14,Fand live more independently."
OL,16,FHe told the Press Association the
OL,17,Fheadset is "very unique" and they hope
OL,18,Fto one day release it as a wearable
OL,19,Fdevice similar to a cap.
