OL,3,C'Unique' AI-powered headset that can
OL,4,Cpredict epilepsy seizures developed
OL,6,FHe said: "We want it to be as discreet
OL,7,Fas possible, to be wireless, light -
OL,8,Fit is a lot of features that none of
OL,9,Fthe other tools right now have."
OL,11,FThe system was trained using thousands
OL,12,Fof hours of historical
OL,13,Felectroencephalography and
OL,14,Felectrocardiography recordings.
OL,16,FThe researchers also used a custom-
OL,17,Fmade "phantom head", attaching
OL,18,Felectrodes to it to simulate a real
OL,19,Fuser.
