OL,3,C'Unique' AI-powered headset that can
OL,4,Cpredict epilepsy seizures developed
OL,6,FBy learning to identify the subtle
OL,7,Felectrical and physiological patterns
OL,8,Fthat precede a seizure, the AI can
OL,9,Fissue a timely alert, giving patients
OL,10,Fand families crucial minutes to
OL,11,Fprepare and stay safe.
OL,13,FIt has an accuracy of up to 95%, and
OL,14,Fthe AI algorithm can display its
OL,15,Flevels of confidence about the chances
OL,16,Fof an impending seizure.
OL,18,FProf Larijani added: "For families
OL,19,Faffected by epilepsy, even a brief
OL,20,Fwarning means they can prevent
OL,21,Finjuries and reduce fear.
