OL,4,Cpredict epilepsy seizures developed
OL,6,FDue to the need for regulatory
OL,7,Fapprovals, it will likely be some
OL,8,Fyears before the product becomes
OL,9,Fwidely available.
OL,11,FProf Larijani said: "The most
OL,12,Fregulated things are medical devices.
OL,13,FIt takes time to get through the
OL,14,Fhurdles.
OL,16,F"But I think we've done the initial
OL,17,Ffeasibility testing both on the
OL,18,Fsoftware and the hardware
OL,19,Fcharacteristics.
